Title: L-DK Hitotsu Yane no Shita, (Suki) ga Futatsu
Actors: Shiori Akita, Mone Kamishiraishi, Keita Machida, Yôsuke Sugino
Plot: Aoi Nishimori and Shusei Kugayama are in love and they begin to live together secretly. Suddenly, Shusei's cousin Reon Kugayama comes to them. Their secret is discovered by Reon. Now, Aoi, Shusei and Reon begin to live together.
